pyhole - A modular IRC bot for Python developers.


Core Requirements

    - Python 2.5+
    - Eventlet


Plugin Requirements

    - BeautifulSoup
    - launchpadlib
    - pywapi
    - simplejson


Test Requirements

    - nose

Installation

    git clone git://github.com/jk0/pyhole.git
    cd pyhole
    cp pyhole.conf.example pyhole.conf
    vi pyhole.conf

    ./bin/pyhole
